title: New board of directors announced for Service New Brunswick (Government of New Brunswick)
text: ( Source : Government of New Brunswick ) FREDERICTON ( GNB ) - The provincial government announced the appointment of a new board of directors for Service New Brunswick . 'I am pleased to welcome these new members,' said Ed Doherty , minister
